            "title": "立足股壇｜利是股吉利跑贏大市｜JK爸爸（陳立展）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jbh25HO33zPv1hswbJCY.g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/7b5b13bbd2c0f70543b37dbfe1098119\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股周四再次失守牛熊分界的250天線，但現時造淡的值博率不高，期結日或之前反彈重上25,000點的機會較大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於4月的恒指框架，初步料介乎24,000點至26,500點，故下行空間仍在，惟仍須等待3月期結後最新的資金盤路作確認。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，本年度4隻利是股之一的吉利汽車（175）近期表現明顯跑贏大市，惟股價升越21元後便應先沽三分之一持貨獲利，但預期後市有力再創高位，故不宜悉數沽出。投資者也可部署行使價在22元的沽出認購期權（Short Call）。若成功鎖定利潤可同時部署行使價19元的沽出認沽期權（Short Put），等候在低位再次接貨。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cc39c6b4-fb40-351a-8b90-239d798f9f29-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">快手（1024）績後跌14%，周四收市報45.6元。不過，快手的股價低於50元具值搏率，但投資者可先待股價跌定後再分注吸納。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泡泡瑪特（9992）今年收入指引令市場失望，遭大行削目標價。泡泡瑪特近兩日股價已累跌三成，但投資者可待大市再下跌時，市場對泡泡瑪特的樂觀情緒進一步消退時，才入市更為理想。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>陳立展（JK爸爸</strong>）<br/><strong>獨立股評人<br/>資深期權投資者</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p></div>",
